{"tid":1581770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(聞到雨革陣味)說好的死線呢？","createTime":"2019-09-19T17:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T21:36:45.000Z","uid":176935,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd43102de42a31049a99b1ded9e289a42b34cb3","tid":1581770,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"6月初初發夢果陣<br />\n有班巴打好醒咁話，唔set死線就又變雨革。<br />\n係連登同公海投票幾點死線<br />\n政府唔回應就升級<br />\n<br />\n最近已經無左死線呢回事<br />\n而且被軍政府主導晒<br />\n連登每日就係一大堆無FC既消息<br />\n<br />\n再唔改變 真係會輸"},{"pid":"9b6d838a347259dac6fcc641bc6f6fde0cbfde55","tid":1581770,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=87bbf8a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"0d54b17a2cd388b773c2f75774aa6e441793377e","tid":1581770,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"192d0c8b97040be0ff828a1921ab2738967ab292","tid":1581770,"uid":62167,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"死線唔難<br />\n仲點升級？<br />\n92 93 罷工已經少左一堆人"},{"pid":"50595d860e1dea20a56156035c44a371f844d5ab","tid":1581770,"uid":141508,"like":2,"dislik